register.description: GIO power down mode register

bitfield.description: Writing to the GIOPWDN bit is only allowed in privilege mode. Reading of the GIOPWDN bit is allowed in all modes. Privilege mode (write): 0 = Normal operation; clocks enabled to GIO module 1 = Power-down mode User mode (write): Writes have no effect in user mode. User or privilege mode (read): 0 = Normal operation; clocks enabled to GIO module 1 = Power-down mode
